UID:Gkuz0kBGWT3AsitEFXFtn
SUMMARY:Clock-Out Lounge Presents: The Darts- U.S. (Album Release) w/ Servi
	ce plus Dish Pit
DTSTAMP:20260326T024946Z
DTSTART:20260509T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Clock-Out Lounge Presents: The Darts- U.S. (Album Release) Serv
	ice plus Dish Pit Saturday May 9th8:30 PM 21+ $17 adv/ $20 dos https://the
	dartsus.bandcamp.com/track/apocalypse-singleGarage-punk-rock grrls will ma
	ke your head slam and your feet shake. And then theres the music.https://g
	immesomeservice.bandcamp.com/album/drag-me-3S-E-R-V-I-C-E is a rock and ro
	ll band for fans of The Fall\\\, The Stooges\\\, Ike and Tina\\\, bad tast
	e\\\, Bukowski\\\, ranch water\\\, and standing in line reading tabloids a
